## Common Pitfalls

```
❌ import { SafeAreaView } from 'react-native'
✅ import { SafeAreaView } from 'react-native-safe-area-context'

❌ <Stack.Screen name="bibleschool" />
✅ <Stack.Screen name="bibleschool/index" />  (full path)

❌ router.push('/(main)/bibleschool')
✅ router.push(routes.bibleschool())

❌ useEffect + setState for data fetching
✅ useQuery / useMutation from TanStack Query

❌ expo-av Video component
✅ expo-video

❌ KeyboardAvoidingView + ScrollView for forms
✅ FormScrollView from @/components/ui/FormScrollView

❌ Hardcoded strings: <Text>Laden...</Text>
✅ <Text>{t('common.loading')}</Text>

❌ null for optional values
✅ undefined for optional values

❌ Translate to only en.json / nl.json
✅ Add to all 5 locale files: en, nl, bg, hi, id

❌ Hardcoded hex colors
✅ theme.* tokens from useTheme()

❌ ActivityIndicator for full-screen loading
✅ LoadingScreen from @/components/ui/LoadingScreen

❌ Direct supabase calls in components
✅ Service methods + TanStack Query
```

